data.description: Welcome Home! Move right into this One Level Ranch Style Home Nestled in the charming enclave of Lake Casse. This 2-Bedrooms plus Den,2 Full Baths, Beautiful Updated Kitchen W/ Granite Countertops & SS Appliances, Updated Bath with Seamless Glass Shower Door, Spacious Living Rm W/ Wood Stove insert & Bay Window, Hardwood Floors throughout the 1st Level, the lower Level offers a Full Finished Walkout to Level Yard perfect for entertaining, Large Shed. This Home is part of the Private Lake Casse Community which offers a large private beach, picnic tables, playground and a roomy clubhouse for private parties. Experience the epitome of comfort, style, and convenience in this charming lakeside retreat. Schedule your tour today and make this gem yours before it's gone!  Walk to Rail-trail, conveniently close to shopping, Schools, 684 & Train. *Multiple Offers, sellers are requesting Final & Best by Tuesday 4/16 at 12 Noon.
